4 3. Be permitted to transfer its products from the processor premises to
5 the location where those retail sales occur without having to transfer
6 physical possession of those regulated adult-use products to a licensed
7 wholesaler in accordance with the following:
8 a. Without otherwise reporting those regulated adult-use products
