9 false, fraudulent, or altered identification card, paper, or any other document to
10 purchase or attempt to purchase or otherwise obtain any regulated adult-use
11 products. A person who violates this section shall for the first offense be guilty of
12 a violation and, for the second and each subsequent offense, be guilty of a Class
13 B misdemeanor.
